item.title: CVE-2011-2515|2024-08-06T23:00:34.249Z -- packagekit -- packagekit
item.description: PackageKit 0.6.17 allows installation of unsigned RPM packages as though they were signed which may allow installation of non-trusted packages and execution of arbitrary code.
